      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Here's a fantastic opportunity to get behind the wheel of a genuinely well-maintained vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use, runs reliably, and has been cared for throughout its life. You'll appreciate the solid mechanicals and clean overall presentation without paying mint-condition prices. A smart buy for anyone who wants quality and dependability without breaking the bank!",
