      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice some scratches, paint fade in certain areas, and a few minor dents that are cosmetically imperfect but don't affect the structural integrity of the vehicle. The interior has seen regular use, with worn upholstery on the seats, some scuffs on the door panels, and general wear on the dashboard surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 expect that routine maintenance items could be due or upcoming. It's not a showroom vehicle, but it's a functional, drivable car that can serve as reliable everyday transportation for a buyer who doesn't mind the cosmetic imperfections and is prepared for the possibility of some maintenance costs down the road. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
      "price": 16000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Mint-Condition Find \u2013 Like Driving It Off the Lot! \ud83c\udf1f\n\nThis is the one you've been waiting for! We're thrilled to offer a vehicle that is in absolutely pristine, mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! Every inch of this car reflects exceptional care: the exterior gleams, the interior is spotless, and everything runs and feels as close to brand-new as you'll find on the used market. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 just a genuinely outstanding vehicle that has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. If you've been searching for a used car that feels anything but 'used,' this is your chance. Come see it in person and experience the difference for yourself \u2014 we're confident you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, best suited for buyers on a tight budget, project enthusiasts, or anyone simply needing basic point-A-to-point-B transportation. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust, dents, and faded or chipped paint throughout. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with age and heavy use. Mechanically, the car runs but should be expected to require repairs \u2014 some systems may be unreliable or in need of attention, and a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended. There are no luxury features or modern conveniences to speak of. This is an honest, no-frills listing for a vehicle that reflects its age and condition. Priced accordingly at $5,000 to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint retains a deep, flawless shine with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. The body panels are perfectly aligned, all trim pieces are intact and gleaming, and the glass is crystal clear without any chips or cracks. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets are spotless, the headliner is pristine, and every button, knob, and screen functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and full mechanical integrity. All scheduled maintenance is up to date, and the vehicle drives with the confidence and smoothness you'd expect from a car in this condition. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic work, no surprises. What you see is exactly what you get.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
